                        <additions>
                            <list>
                                <item xml:id="a1">
                                    <desc type="ProtectivePrayer">Prayers to St Gabriel, St Michael and Our Lady Mary.
                           </desc>
                                    <locus target="#2"/>
                                    <p>Crudely written.</p>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">Ownership Note</desc>
                                    <locus target="#60"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፈ፡ ዘአርከለዲስ፡ ንግዱ፡ ወብእሲቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ገብርኤል፡ ጣይቱ፡ ወውሉዱ፡ ወለተ፡ ሚካኤል፡ አዘነጋሽ፡ ዕሤተ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ወልደ፡ ኪሮስ፡ ወልደ፡ ማርያም፡ 
                                        ወለተ፡ ማርያም፡ መክብበ፡ ሰማዕት።</q>
                                    <q xml:lang="en">This book belongs to ʾArkaladis Nǝgdu; his wife is Walatta Gabrǝʾel Ṭāytu; his sons are Walatta Mikāʾel ʾAzanagāš, ʿƎśeta Mikāʾel, Walda Kiros, Walda Māryām, Walatta Māryām, Makbǝba Samāʿǝt.</q>
                                    <p>The note states that <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11029Arkala">ʾArkaladis Nǝgdu</persName> is the owner of the book and mentions his relatives: his wife 
                                        <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11030WalattaG">Walatta Gabrǝʾel Ṭāytu</persName>, his sons and daughters <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11031WalattaM">Walatta Mikāʾel ʾAzanagāš</persName>, 
                                        <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11032EsetaM">ʿƎseta Mikāʾel</persName>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11033WaldaKi">Walda Kiros</persName>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11034WaldaMa">Walda Māryām</persName>, 
                                        <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11035WalattaM">Walatta Māryām</persName>, and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11036Makbeba">Makbǝba Samāʿǝt</persName>.</p>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="a3">
                                    <desc type="Doxology">Praise to Our Lady Mary</desc>
                                    <locus target="#62"/>
                                    <p>Written in the same hand as that of <ref target="#a2"/>.</p>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="a4">
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">Ownership note</desc>
                                    <locus target="#152"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፈ፡ ዘአርከለዲስ፡ ወብእሲቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ገብርኤል፡ ጣይቱ፡ ንግዱ።</q>
                                    <q xml:lang="en">This book belongs to ʾArkaladis; his wife is Walatta Gabrǝʾel Ṭāytu Nǝgdu; </q>
                                    <p>The note states that <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11029Arkala">ʾArkaladis Nǝgdu</persName> is the owner of the book and mentions his wife <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11030WalattaG">Walatta Gabrǝʾel Ṭāytu</persName>. 
                                        It is written in the same hand as that of <ref target="#a2"/>.</p>
                                </item>
                            </list>
